  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Retail Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Orchard</p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Shift-based (Morning: 9:30am – 6:30pm | Afternoon: 12:30pm – 9:30pm)<br />5-day work week inclusive of weekends & public holidays</p><p><strong>Compensation & Benefits:</strong><br />Basic Salary + Allowances + AWS + Variable Bonuses</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Deliver a personalised, high-touch customer experience through expert product knowledge, styling advice, and wardrobe coordination.</p></li><li><p>Drive sales performance through effective cross-selling and upselling while maintaining brand elegance and service excellence.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong client relationships, including managing a database of regular customers and understanding individual preferences.</p></li><li><p>Oversee daily retail operations including cashiering, stock control, visual standards, housekeeping, and security compliance.</p></li><li><p>Execute visual merchandising in line with brand concepts and provide feedback to maximise sales impact.</p></li><li><p>Conduct stock checks, replenishment, and inventory control to ensure optimal stock availability and accuracy.</p></li><li><p>Mentor and coach retail staff and promoters, upholding luxury service standards, grooming, and professionalism.</p></li><li><p>Handle customer feedback and service recovery with discretion and professionalism.</p></li><li><p>Support omni-channel initiatives, including online store operations and digital marketing activities.</p></li></ul><h3>Why Join My Client </h3><ul><li><p><strong>Work with a premium brand</strong> in a prime Orchard location, representing refined style and exceptional craftsmanship.</p></li><li><p><strong>Elevated client engagement</strong> – build long-term relationships with discerning customers who value personalised service.</p></li><li><p><strong>Career progression opportunities</strong> in a luxury retail environment that recognises performance and leadership potential.</p></li><li><p><strong>Attractive rewards</strong> including allowances, AWS, and performance-based bonuses.</p></li><li><p><strong>Professional development</strong> through structured coaching, mentorship, and exposure to visual merchandising and omni-channel retail operations.</p></li></ul>",
